reduce number of duplicate relationships by only mapping inbound and not outbound, since in the majority (all?) cases there is always an inbound/outbound match
Functionality added to allow running demo without network connection
Best practice is for upper-case relationship labels
Changed so relationship to client - FILED -> filings, which makes more sense from a left-to-right perspective, added some more queries
Changed to load all filings contained within zip file
Documented query files a little better after confirming all queries worked as designed.
